summary: Can I just say how impressed I was with what we’ve seen of the Legendary Birds’ first appearances so far? I’m especially loving...
body:
Can I just say how impressed I was with what we’ve seen of the Legendary Birds’ first appearances so far? I’m especially loving Moltres’s as we see in this clip from Pokemon’s YouTube channel:

[Image Description: Two screenshots from a Pokemon Let’s Go trailer. The first shows Moltres warily circling an awed trainer with a Pikachu on their shoulder, while the second shows Moltres glarting at them, its head close to theirs.]

Having a Moltres circle the trainer and glare in their face really makes them feel intimidating, like a powerful force of nature. They aren’t evil creatures, of course, but they certainly are powerful and not to be taken lightly in battle. 

Ultimately, I’m loving what we’ve seen of the cutscenes so far.

REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.

I hope you enjoy my fusions!

Water/Fairy Type

Ability: Cute Charm

The Cute Winged Pokemon
